# Implementation Walkthrough

We have successfully implemented the requested pages, navigation updates, UI redesigns, and footer integrations.

## 1. User Profile & Settings
- **My Reports Page** ([src/pages/MyReportsPage.tsx](file:///Users/johnoseni/Downloads/Weatherapppelias/src/pages/MyReportsPage.tsx)): Built securely inside the standard Dashboard Layout, allowing users to view and manage their incident reports.
- **Settings Page** ([src/pages/SettingsPage.tsx](file:///Users/johnoseni/Downloads/Weatherapppelias/src/pages/SettingsPage.tsx)): Designed using shadcn `Tabs` to break down settings into "Profile", "Notifications", and "Preferences". 
- **Header Profile Integration**: Added direct routing from the global Header Avatar Dropdown to `My Reports` and [Settings](file:///Users/johnoseni/Downloads/Weatherapppelias/src/pages/SettingsPage.tsx#11-140).

## 2. Landing Page Enhancements
- **How It Works Redesign**: We heavily refactored the "How EcoWatch Works" section in [src/components/landing/LandingSections.tsx](file:///Users/johnoseni/Downloads/Weatherapppelias/src/components/landing/LandingSections.tsx) to feature:
  - Custom branded icons with modern gradients.
  - Floating card animations and hover states that scale the icon and create a shadow drop effect.
  - A subtle connecting pulse line for desktop views mimicking a structured workflow.
  - Much more professional typography, mimicking modern SaaS layouts.

## 3. The Footer & Dialogs
We refactored [src/components/layout/Footer.tsx](file:///Users/johnoseni/Downloads/Weatherapppelias/src/components/layout/Footer.tsx) extensively:
- **Removed Links**: Removed dead links for "Careers" and "Mobile App".
- **Pop-up Dialogs**: Implemented sleek shadcn Dialog flows for "Partnerships" and "Research" inquiries directly triggered from the footer link clicks. These feature fully functional form fields and success toast notifications upon submission.
- **Coming Soon Flags**: Added `toast.info(...)` popup triggers indicating that API Access, Documentation, Data Downloads, and Press Kit are "coming soon".

## 4. Institutional & Legal Pages
Created beautiful, easily readable static pages conforming to our design system:
- **About Us** (`/about`): Outlining our core mission.
- **Privacy Policy** (`/privacy`)
- **Terms of Service** (`/terms`)
- **Data Policy** (`/data-policy`)
- **Cookie Policy** (`/cookies`)

All of the above have been wired up into the `<BrowserRouter>` in [App.tsx](file:///Users/johnoseni/Downloads/Weatherapppelias/src/App.tsx) and linked correctly in the Footer component.

## Validation
- Successfully ran TypeScript compiler (`tsc`) and Vite build.
- The React Router dynamically lazy loads these routes seamlessly as part of the overall page bundle without throwing 404s.
